## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff854-159">下面的代码示例将的几何转换重置 `pgBrush` 为标识。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff854-159">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ff854-160">假定 `myPath` 是现有的 <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff854-160">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
